<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3423] hbase-env.sh over-rides HBASE_OPTS incorrectly.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3423</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf/hbase-env.sh has the following line:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   export HBASE_OPTS=&quot;-ea -XX:+HeapDumpOnOutOfMemoryError -XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC -XX:+CMSIncrementalMode&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should be&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   export HBASE_OPTS=&quot;$HBASE_OPTS -ea -XX:+HeapDumpOnOutOfMemoryError -XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC -XX:+CMSIncrementalMode&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
